citations:
    citation-asos-jaime-iv:
        source: source-asos
        properties:
            locator: "Jaime IV"
            text_from_source: "His hand was always between them. Urswyck had hung it about his neck on a cord... They took my sword hand. Was that all I was, a sword hand? Gods be good, is it true?"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Jaime's recovery chapter. He and Brienne are transported to Harrenhal by Vargo Hoat's men. Arrives at Harrenhal where Roose Bolton is in command. Jaime meets Qyburn, who cleans and tends his ruined stump. Sapphires incident where Jaime saves Brienne from rape by shouting 'Sapphires!'"
